<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Royal Chronicles of War | Prince Patawat</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@600&family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    background: #0f0f0f;
    color: #f5f5f5;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
}

header {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #1a1a1a);
    padding: 25px 15px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid gold;
}

header h1 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    color: gold;
    font-size: 28px;
}

header p {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: #ccc;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px;
}

.section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 40px 0 20px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: gold;
    border-bottom: 1px solid gold;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 5px;
}

.grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
}

.card {
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,215,0,0.2);
    transition: 0.4s;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255,215,0,0.5);
}

.card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
}

.card-content {
    padding: 15px;
}

.card h3 {
    color: gold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
}

.card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border-top: 2px solid gold;
    margin-top: 40px;
    background: #000;
    font-size: 14px;
}

@media(max-width: 600px) {
    header h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Royal Chronicles of War</h1>
    <p>Curated & Presented by Prince Patawat</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

<h2 class="section-title">Major World Wars</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6c/Battle_of_Agincourt.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Hundred Years' War</h3>
<p><strong>Leaders:</strong> Edward III, Henry V, Charles VII</p>
<p><strong>Cities:</strong> Orléans, Paris</p>
<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Longbows, swords, early cannons</p>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Dynastic struggle between England and France (1337–1453).</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/WWI_Soldiers.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>World War I</h3>
<p><strong>Leaders:</strong> Kaiser Wilhelm II, Woodrow Wilson</p>
<p><strong>Cities:</strong> Sarajevo, Verdun</p>
<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Rifles, tanks, poison gas</p>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Global conflict reshaping Europe (1914–1918).</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a8/Bundesarchiv_Bild_101I-646-5188-17%2C_Russland%2C_Kesselschlacht_Stalingrad.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>World War II</h3>
<p><strong>Leaders:</strong> Churchill, Roosevelt, Hitler, Stalin</p>
<p><strong>Cities:</strong> Berlin, Stalingrad, Hiroshima</p>
<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Tanks, aircraft, atomic bombs</p>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Largest war in human history (1939–1945).</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<h2 class="section-title">Historic Indian Wars</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5e/First_Battle_of_Panipat_1526.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>First Battle of Panipat (1526)</h3>
<p><strong>Leaders:</strong> Babur vs Ibrahim Lodi</p>
<p><strong>City:</strong> Panipat</p>
<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Matchlock guns, artillery</p>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Foundation of the Mughal Empire in India.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4f/Haldighati.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Battle of Haldighati (1576)</h3>
<p><strong>Leaders:</strong> Maharana Pratap vs Man Singh I</p>
<p><strong>Location:</strong> Haldighati, Rajasthan</p>
<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Swords, spears, cavalry</p>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Symbol of Rajput valor and resistance.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/Battle_of_Plassey_1757.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Battle of Plassey (1757)</h3>
<p><strong>Leaders:</strong> Siraj-ud-Daulah vs Robert Clive</p>
<p><strong>City:</strong> Plassey</p>
<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Muskets, cannons</p>
<p><strong>Summary:</strong> Marked the beginning of British dominance in India.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

